<!-- ─── TIMER TAB ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<div id="tab-timer" class="tab-panel active">
  <div class="section-header">
    <h2><span data-lang="en">How long can I stay in the sun?</span><span data-lang="zh">我能在阳光下待多久？</span><span data-lang="ko">햇볕 아래 얼마나 있을 수 있나요?</span><span data-lang="ja">太陽の下にどのくらい居られますか？</span></h2>
    <p><span data-lang="en">Enter your skin type, UV index, and sunscreen SPF to estimate your safe sun exposure time. Based on the Fitzpatrick scale and Minimal Erythemal Dose (MED).</span><span data-lang="zh">输入您的皮肤类型、紫外线指数和防晒系数，估算安全日晒时间。基于菲茨帕特里克量表和最小红斑剂量（MED）。</span><span data-lang="ko">피부 유형, 자외선 지수, SPF를 입력하여 안전한 햇볕 노출 시간을 추정하세요. 피츠패트릭 척도와 최소 홍반량(MED)을 기반으로 합니다.</span><span data-lang="ja">皮膚タイプ、UVインデックス、SPFを入力して安全な日光暴露時間を推定します。フィッツパトリックスケールと最小紅斑量（MED）に基づいています。</span></p>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="timer-grid">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label><span data-lang="en">Skin type</span><span data-lang="zh">皮肤类型</span><span data-lang="ko">피부 유형</span><span data-lang="ja">皮膚タイプ</span></label>
        <select id="skinType" onchange="calculate()">
          <option value="1" data-en="Type I — always burns, never tans" data-zh="I型 — 总是晒红，从不晒黑" data-ko="I형 — 항상 화상, 절대 태닝 안 됨" data-ja="Iタイプ — 常に日焼け、色褐化なし"></option>
          <option value="2" data-en="Type II — usually burns, tans minimally" data-zh="II型 — 通常晒红，轻微晒黑" data-ko="II형 — 자주 화상, 약간 태닝" data-ja="IIタイプ — よく日焼け、わずかに色褐化"></option>
          <option value="3" selected data-en="Type III — sometimes burns, tans gradually" data-zh="III型 — 有时晒红，逐渐晒黑" data-ko="III형 — 때로 화상, 서서히 태닝" data-ja="IIIタイプ — 時々日焼け、徐々に色褐化"></option>
          <option value="4" data-en="Type IV — rarely burns, tans easily" data-zh="IV型 — 很少晒红，容易晒黑" data-ko="IV형 — 화상 드묾, 쉽게 태닝" data-ja="IVタイプ — めったに日焼けしない、簡単に色褐化"></option>
          <option value="5" data-en="Type V — very rarely burns, tans deeply" data-zh="V型 — 极少晒红，深度晒黑" data-ko="V형 — 거의 화상 없음, 깊은 태닝" data-ja="Vタイプ — ほとんど日焼けしない、深く色褐化"></option>
          <option value="6" data-en="Type VI — never burns, deeply pigmented" data-zh="VI型 — 从不晒红，肤色深" data-ko="VI형 — 화상 없음, 매우 짙은 피부" data-ja="VIタイプ — 日焼けしない、深い色素"></option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label><span data-lang="en">UV index now</span><span data-lang="zh">当前紫外线指数</span><span data-lang="ko">현재 자외선 지수</span><span data-lang="ja">現在のUVインデックス</span></label>
        <select id="uvIndex" onchange="calculate()">
          <option value="1.5" data-en="1–2 (Low)" data-zh="1–2（低）" data-ko="1–2 (낮음)" data-ja="1–2（低い）"></option>
          <option value="3.5" data-en="3–4 (Moderate)" data-zh="3–4（中等）" data-ko="3–4 (보통)" data-ja="3–4（中程度）"></option>
          <option value="5.5" selected data-en="5–6 (High)" data-zh="5–6（高）" data-ko="5–6 (높음)" data-ja="5–6（高い）"></option>
          <option value="8" data-en="7–9 (Very High)" data-zh="7–9（非常高）" data-ko="7–9 (매우 높음)" data-ja="7–9（非常に高い）"></option>
          <option value="11" data-en="10–11+ (Extreme)" data-zh="10–11+（极端）" data-ko="10–11+ (매우 위험)" data-ja="10–11+（非常に危険）"></option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label><span data-lang="en">Sunscreen SPF</span><span data-lang="zh">防晒霜 SPF</span><span data-lang="ko">선크림 SPF</span><span data-lang="ja">日焼け止め SPF</span></label>
        <select id="spf" onchange="calculate()">
          <option value="1" data-en="No sunscreen" data-zh="无防晒霜" data-ko="선크림 없음" data-ja="日焼け止めなし"></option>
          <option value="3.75" data-en="SPF 15" data-zh="SPF 15" data-ko="SPF 15" data-ja="SPF 15"></option>
          <option value="7.5" data-en="SPF 30" data-zh="SPF 30" data-ko="SPF 30" data-ja="SPF 30"></option>
          <option value="12.5" selected data-en="SPF 50 (recommended)" data-zh="SPF 50（推荐）" data-ko="SPF 50 (권장)" data-ja="SPF 50（推奨）"></option>
          <option value="14" data-en="SPF 50+" data-zh="SPF 50+" data-ko="SPF 50+" data-ja="SPF 50+"></option>
        </select>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="uv-scale">
      <div class="uv-scale-label"><span data-lang="en">UV index scale</span><span data-lang="zh">紫外线指数刻度</span><span data-lang="ko">자외선 지수 척도</span><span data-lang="ja">UVインデックス目盛り</span></div>
      <div class="uv-track"><div class="uv-pin" id="uvPin" style="left:42%"></div></div>
      <div class="uv-labels">
        <span data-lang="en">Low</span><span data-lang="zh">低</span><span data-lang="ko">낮음</span><span data-lang="ja">低</span>
        <span data-lang="en">Moderate</span><span data-lang="zh">中等</span><span data-lang="ko">보통</span><span data-lang="ja">中</span>
        <span data-lang="en">High</span><span data-lang="zh">高</span><span data-lang="ko">높음</span><span data-lang="ja">高</span>
        <span data-lang="en">Very High</span><span data-lang="zh">非常高</span><span data-lang="ko">매우 높음</span><span data-lang="ja">非常に高</span>
        <span data-lang="en">Extreme</span><span data-lang="zh">极端</span><span data-lang="ko">위험</span><span data-lang="ja">危険</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="resultCard" class="result-card caution">
      <div class="result-time" id="resultTime">—</div>
      <div class="result-sublabel" id="resultLabel"><span data-lang="en">Fill in your details above</span><span data-lang="zh">请在上方填写您的信息</span><span data-lang="ko">위에 정보를 입력하세요</span><span data-lang="ja">上の情報を入力してください</span></div>
    </div>
    <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-light);text-align:center;margin:-8px 0 16px;line-height:1.6;">
      <span data-lang="en">Based on Fitzpatrick MED values &amp; WHO UV irradiance formula (UVI × 0.025 W/m²). Real-world SPF effectiveness applied. This is an estimate — individual responses vary.</span>
      <span data-lang="zh">基于菲茨帕特里克MED值和世卫组织紫外线辐照度公式。已应用实际SPF效果。此为估算值，个体差异可能不同。</span>
      <span data-lang="ko">피츠패트릭 MED 값과 WHO 자외선 조도 공식(UVI × 0.025 W/m²) 기반. 실제 SPF 효과 적용. 추정값이며 개인차가 있습니다.</span>
      <span data-lang="ja">フィッツパトリックMED値とWHO UV照射公式に基づく。実際のSPF効果を適用。推定値であり個人差があります。</span>
    </div>
    <div class="alert alert-warn" style="margin-bottom:16px;">
      <strong><span data-lang="en">⚠ Taking photosensitising medications? </span><span data-lang="zh">⚠ 正在服用光敏性药物？</span><span data-lang="ko">⚠ 광과민성 약물 복용 중? </span><span data-lang="ja">⚠ 光感受性の薬を服用中？</span></strong>
      <span data-lang="en">Your actual burn time may be much shorter than this estimate. See the <strong>My Medications</strong> tab for details.</span>
      <span data-lang="zh">您的实际晒伤时间可能远短于此估算值。详情请查看<strong>我的药物</strong>选项卡。</span>
      <span data-lang="ko">실제 화상 시간은 이 추정값보다 훨씬 짧을 수 있습니다. <strong>나의 약물</strong> 탭을 참조하세요.</span>
      <span data-lang="ja">実際の日焼け時間はこの推定値より短い場合があります。<strong>わたしの薬</strong>タブをご覧ください。</span>
    </div>
    <div class="timer-widget">
      <div class="ring-container">
        <svg class="ring-svg" width="140" height="140" viewBox="0 0 140 140">
          <circle class="ring-bg" cx="70" cy="70" r="60"/>
          <circle class="ring-progress" id="ringProgress" cx="70" cy="70" r="60"/>
        </svg>
        <div class="ring-center"><div class="ring-num" id="ringNum">—</div><div class="ring-unit" id="ringUnit">min</div></div>
      </div>
      <button class="timer-btn" id="timerBtn" onclick="toggleTimer()">
        <span id="timerBtnText"><span data-lang="en">▶ Start timer</span><span data-lang="zh">▶ 开始计时</span><span data-lang="ko">▶ 타이머 시작</span><span data-lang="ja">▶ タイマー開始</span></span>
      </button>
      <div class="timer-msg" id="timerMsg"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="alert alert-info">
    <strong><span data-lang="en">Sydney UV today — </span><span data-lang="zh">今日悉尼紫外线 — </span><span data-lang="ko">오늘 시드니 자외선 — </span><span data-lang="ja">今日のシドニーUV — </span></strong>
    <span data-lang="en">UV is typically High to Very High in summer (Oct–Mar). Check the <a href="https://www.bom.gov.au/uv/" target="_blank">Bureau of Meteorology UV forecast</a> before going outdoors.</span>
    <span data-lang="zh">夏季（10月至3月）紫外线通常为高至非常高。外出前请查看<a href="https://www.bom.gov.au/uv/" target="_blank">气象局紫外线预报</a>。</span>
    <span data-lang="ko">여름(10월~3월)에는 자외선이 높음에서 매우 높음 수준입니다. 외출 전 <a href="https://www.bom.gov.au/uv/" target="_blank">기상청 자외선 예보</a>를 확인하세요.</span>
    <span data-lang="ja">夏（10月〜3月）はUV指数が高くなります。外出前に<a href="https://www.bom.gov.au/uv/" target="_blank">気象局のUV予報</a>を確認してください。</span>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ─── MEDS TAB ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<div id="tab-meds" class="tab-panel">
  <div class="section-header"><h2><span data-lang="en">Medications that cause photosensitivity</span><span data-lang="zh">引起光敏反应的药物</span><span data-lang="ko">광과민성을 유발하는 약물</span><span data-lang="ja">光感受性を引き起こす薬</span></h2></div>
  <div class="alert alert-warn"><strong><span data-lang="en">Important — </span><span data-lang="zh">重要提示 — </span><span data-lang="ko">중요 — </span><span data-lang="ja">重要 — </span></strong><span data-lang="en">Photosensitivity reactions can cause severe sunburn-like rashes, blistering, or lasting skin discolouration — even on cloudy days or through windows. Do not stop your medication without speaking to your doctor.</span><span data-lang="zh">光敏反应可导致严重的类似晒伤皮疹、起泡或持续性皮肤变色——即使在阴天或隔窗也可能发生。未经医生同意，请勿停药。</span><span data-lang="ko">광과민성 반응은 흐린 날이나 창문을 통해서도 심한 일광화상 유사 발진, 물집, 또는 지속적인 피부 변색을 유발할 수 있습니다. 의사 상담 없이 약을 중단하지 마세요.</span><span data-lang="ja">光感受性反応は、曇りの日や窓越しでも、重篤な日焼けに似た発疹、水疱、または皮膚変色を引き起こすことがあります。医師の相談なしに薬を中止しないでください。</span></div>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title"><span data-lang="en">Common photosensitising medications</span><span data-lang="zh">常见光敏性药物</span><span data-lang="ko">흔한 광과민성 약물</span><span data-lang="ja">一般的な光感受性の薬</span></div>
    <div class="meds-grid">
      <div class="med-card"><div class="med-category"><span data-lang="en">Antibiotics</span><span data-lang="zh">抗生素</span><span data-lang="ko">항생제</span><span data-lang="ja">抗生物質</span></div><div class="med-name"><span data-lang="en">Tetracyclines</span><span data-lang="zh">四环素类</span><span data-lang="ko">테트라사이클린</span><span data-lang="ja">テトラサイクリン系</span><span class="risk-pill risk-high"><span data-lang="en">High</span><span data-lang="zh">高</span><span data-lang="ko">높음</span><span data-lang="ja">高</span></span></div><div class="med-desc"><span data-lang="en">Doxycycline, minocycline, tetracycline. Commonly used for acne — strongly photosensitising.</span><span data-lang="zh">强力霉素、美满霉素、四环素。常用于治疗痤疮——强光敏性。</span><span data-lang="ko">독시사이클린, 미노사이클린, 테트라사이클린. 여드름 치료에 흔히 사용 — 강한 광과민성.</span><span data-lang="ja">ドキシサイクリン、ミノサイクリン、テトラサイクリン。ニキビ治療に一般的 — 強い光感受性。</span></div></div>
      <div class="med-card"><div class="med-category"><span data-lang="en">Antibiotics</span><span data-lang="zh">抗生素</span><span data-lang="ko">항생제</span><span data-lang="ja">抗生物質</span></div><div class="med-name"><span data-lang="en">Fluoroquinolones</span><span data-lang="zh">氟喹诺酮类</span><span data-lang="ko">플루오로퀴놀론</span><span data-lang="ja">フルオロキノロン系</span><span class="risk-pill risk-mod"><span data-lang="en">Moderate</span><span data-lang="zh">中等</span><span data-lang="ko">중간</span><span data-lang="ja">中程度</span></span></div><div class="med-desc"><span data-lang="en">Ciprofloxacin, norfloxacin. Avoid prolonged sun during treatment.</span><span data-lang="zh">环丙沙星、诺氟沙星。治疗期间避免长时间日晒。</span><span data-lang="ko">시프로플록사신, 노르플록사신. 치료 중 장시간 햇볕 노출 피하세요.</span><span data-lang="ja">シプロフロキサシン、ノルフロキサシン。治療中は長時間の日光を避けてください。</span></div></div>
      <div class="med-card"><div class="med-category"><span data-lang="en">Blood pressure / Diuretics</span><span data-lang="zh">血压 / 利尿剂</span><span data-lang="ko">혈압 / 이뇨제</span><span data-lang="ja">血圧 / 利尿薬</span></div><div class="med-name"><span data-lang="en">Thiazide diuretics</span><span data-lang="zh">噻嗪类利尿剂</span><span data-lang="ko">티아지드 이뇨제</span><span data-lang="ja">チアジド系利尿薬</span><span class="risk-pill risk-high"><span data-lang="en">High</span><span data-lang="zh">高</span><span data-lang="ko">높음</span><span data-lang="ja">高</span></span></div><div class="med-desc"><span data-lang="en">Hydrochlorothiazide, indapamide. Very common blood pressure medication — significant photosensitivity risk.</span><span data-lang="zh">氢氯噻嗪、吲达帕胺。非常常见的降压药——显著光敏风险。</span><span data-lang="ko">하이드로클로로티아지드, 인다파미드. 매우 흔한 혈압약 — 상당한 광과민성 위험.</span><span data-lang="ja">ヒドロクロロチアジド、インダパミド。非常に一般的な血圧薬 — 著しい光感受性リスク。</span></div></div>
      <div class="med-card"><div class="med-category"><span data-lang="en">Heart rhythm</span><span data-lang="zh">心律</span><span data-lang="ko">심장 리듬</span><span data-lang="ja">心臓のリズム</span></div><div class="med-name"><span data-lang="en">Amiodarone</span><span data-lang="zh">胺碘酮</span><span data-lang="ko">아미오다론</span><span data-lang="ja">アミオダロン</span><span class="risk-pill risk-high"><span data-lang="en">High</span><span data-lang="zh">高</span><span data-lang="ko">높음</span><span data-lang="ja">高</span></span></div><div class="med-desc"><span data-lang="en">Used for heart rhythm disorders. Causes phototoxicity and blue-grey skin discolouration lasting months after stopping.</span><span data-lang="zh">用于心律失常。引起光毒反应，停药后皮肤可能出现持续数月的蓝灰色变色。</span><span data-lang="ko">심장 리듬 장애에 사용. 광독성을 유발하며 복용 중단 후 수개월간 피부의 청회색 변색이 지속될 수 있습니다.</span><span data-lang="ja">心律障害に使用。光毒性を引き起こし、中止後数ヶ月間、皮膚の青灰色変色が持続する場合があります。</span></div></div>
      <div class="med-card"><div class="med-category"><span data-lang="en">Mental health</span><span data-lang="zh">精神健康</span><span data-lang="ko">정신 건강</span><span data-lang="ja">精神的健康</span></div><div class="med-name"><span data-lang="en">Phenothiazines</span><span data-lang="zh">吩噻嗪类</span><span data-lang="ko">페노티아진</span><span data-lang="ja">フェノチアジン系</span><span class="risk-pill risk-high"><span data-lang="en">High</span><span data-lang="zh">高</span><span data-lang="ko">높음</span><span data-lang="ja">高</span></span></div><div class="med-desc"><span data-lang="en">Chlorpromazine, promethazine. Significant phototoxic and photoallergic reactions possible.</span><span data-lang="zh">氯丙嗪、异丙嗪。可能发生显著的光毒性和光过敏反应。</span><span data-lang="ko">클로르프로마진, 프로메타진. 상당한 광독성 및 광알레르기 반응이 가능합니다.</span><span data-lang="ja">クロルプロマジン、プロメタジン。著しい光毒性および光アレルギー反応の可能性があります。</span></div></div>
