      <div class="med-card"><div class="med-category"><span data-lang="en">Diabetes</span><span data-lang="zh">糖尿病</span><span data-lang="ko">당뇨</span><span data-lang="ja">糖尿病</span></div><div class="med-name"><span data-lang="en">Sulfonylureas</span><span data-lang="zh">磺脲类</span><span data-lang="ko">설포닐우레아</span><span data-lang="ja">スルホニル尿素系</span><span class="risk-pill risk-mod"><span data-lang="en">Moderate</span><span data-lang="zh">中等</span><span data-lang="ko">중간</span><span data-lang="ja">中程度</span></span></div><div class="med-desc"><span data-lang="en">Glibenclamide, glipizide. Photosensitivity reactions possible, more common at higher doses.</span><span data-lang="zh">格列本脲、格列吡嗪。可能发生光敏反应，剂量较高时更常见。</span><span data-lang="ko">글리벤클라미드, 글리피지드. 광과민성 반응 가능, 고용량에서 더 흔합니다.</span><span data-lang="ja">グリベンクラミド、グリピジド。光感受性反応の可能性、高用量でより一般的。</span></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-title"><span data-lang="en">Two types of reactions</span><span data-lang="zh">两种反应类型</span><span data-lang="ko">두 가지 반응 유형</span><span data-lang="ja">2種類の反応</span></div>
    <div class="reaction-grid">
      <div class="reaction-box phototoxic"><div class="reaction-title"><span data-lang="en">Phototoxic reaction</span><span data-lang="zh">光毒性反应</span><span data-lang="ko">광독성 반응</span><span data-lang="ja">光毒性反応</span></div><p><span data-lang="en">Like a severe exaggerated sunburn. Affects most people on the medication. Occurs within minutes to hours of UV exposure. Most common type.</span><span data-lang="zh">类似严重的夸大晒伤。影响大多数服用该药物的人。在紫外线照射后数分钟至数小时内发生。最常见类型。</span><span data-lang="ko">심한 일광화상처럼 나타납니다. 해당 약물을 복용하는 대부분의 사람에게 영향을 미칩니다. 자외선 노출 후 수분에서 수시간 내에 발생합니다.</span><span data-lang="ja">重篤な誇張した日焼けのようなもの。薬を服用しているほとんどの人に影響します。UV暴露後数分から数時間で発生します。</span></p></div>
